{"tid":453660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「行走的企業」IU當選對經紀公司貢獻最大藝人","createTime":"2017-10-31T11:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T16:20:37.000Z","uid":34643,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"24efb6c17012b1cea832fa0818668686e68f8c84","tid":453660,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/005BDVz9ly1fl17zd5mdgj30eg0o2q59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F005BDVz9ly1fl17zd5mdgj30eg0o2q59.jpg&h=e4968fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　韓國tvN電視台《2017名單公布》節目昨晚發布對經紀公司貢獻最大藝人排行榜，女歌手IU排在了第一位。<br />\n<br />\n　　IU在經歷20多次的選秀落榜後於2008年通過現在的經紀公司LOEN Entertainment，十個月後便出道，短短一年後的2010年以一首《好日子》大紅大紫，僅一年為公司創收超過100億韓元，讓公司在第二年就搬到了6層樓的新辦公大樓。為了答謝IU為公司做出的貢獻，她的經紀公司特意劃出一整層作為IU的訓練室，而IU也投桃報李，在沒有契約金的情況下與公司簽訂了為期三年的續約協議。直至現在為止，IU仍是韓國歌壇最炙手可熱的solo女歌手，獲得許多出演電視劇和廣告的機會，還被稱為「行走的企業」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006hTriOly1fl1a90nszrj30ku112k4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006hTriOly1fl1a90nszrj30ku112k4b.jpg&h=39e6bf21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7922cc65706067ceb79dd536c07d62aaf559eec","tid":453660,"uid":8612,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"轉會yg就正"},{"pid":"8484e2733d9b10b3d068d51ee16e6c308216302f","tid":453660,"uid":60286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"係其他公司未必會咁紅<br />\n<br />\n感恩LOEN俾IU咁多資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36c54d8b3f85af4378b0936d09f96574658c7e7","tid":453660,"uid":33176,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯行走的風俗業"},{"pid":"237d8281403e94852443bb0bc67c5acb265fb26c","tid":453660,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係其他公司未必會咁紅<br />\n<br />\