,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯行走的風俗業</blockquote><br />\n差好遠喎，曲線都曲靚啲丫"},{"pid":"2c90dd540b9ef54634d874de67bab05de2e7d250","tid":453660,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"loen 好疊水嫁喎<br />\n除左三大其他人d 碟通常就係loen 同mnet 出"},{"pid":"b1c8cfed61cb27d3ac58a80fd78969d4e901b04a","tid":453660,"uid":34229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"Iu bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa82b6686e33773b995b438152397dd96f09122","tid":453660,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>loen 好疊水嫁喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左三大其他人d 碟通常就係loen 同mnet 出</blockquote><br />\nloen主要做唱片發行 又有melon 所以賺錢厲害 在娛樂企劃方面一直差勁 基本是靠IU才有現在的知名度 loen後來藝人部單獨設為loen tree 不久改名叫fave 但老飯還是習慣稱IU是loen公司的 fave與其他子公司的區別也簡單 fave是loen親生的 其他是買的 ​<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/61ad358bgy1fl1s2yqtbxj20im205jx8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F61ad358bgy1fl1s2yqtbxj20im205jx8.jpg&h=31ce61f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司市值比3大高, 但娛樂企劃唔夠3大黎"},{"pid":"7fd1ac55f589e8e890622ef757b9a6f5c4ab0341","tid":453660,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"其實LOEN本身就係大公司黎, 印象中市值仲高過3大, 但佢主力係做唱片發行<br />\n<br />\n如果單計經紀部門 咁的確係靠IU一個撐起"},{"pid":"7a5665550d08b4dcbbebdd1623a0db2c5f80ccac","tid":453660,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">李知恩世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}